  Locus:
    Page: 251
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Humility
---
Humility is the highest of all virtues. You can destroy your egotism by
developing this virtue alone. You can influence people. You can become
a magnet to attract the world. It must be genuine. Feigned humility is
hypocrisy.
